{
  "stem": "20088.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, everything was really difficult and impossible, but somehow we got-- we were able to do those things which we're not allowed to.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went to this hospital where the treatment was, but I ran off and I went to this block where I knew Mini was and my mother.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that time at the last shower, which we got, I got a huge, very, very heavy men's coat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was all I had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was my clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was at least warm, but I could hardly carry myself with it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was very, very cold, and I got into this block where Mini was and they were on-- at the end of the block where they worked at a an office, but there was a little hole, a little space where they had some medicine and some paperwork and things.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said to-- I went to her and said, Mini.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She didn't recognize me at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I said, I'm [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Evi. ?] Oh, ha, ha, ha.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She said, oh, I must go and-- come, come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Must tell your mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was very red because of from the cold, and with this big coat I looked quite healthy and-- and strong.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she took me there, and in the hospital blocks there were just bunk beds-- two, not those with 10 people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Just two on top of each other, but two people slept in each one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and my mother was on the top bunk quite weak and not very well, and my mother-- then Fritzi, I've got somebody here to show you.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother crawled down and saw me in this enormous coat and red, and she-- she kind of came down very weak, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was difficult.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
